0not%20getting%20enough%20work%20and%20was%20suffering%20from%20depression.%20The%20family%20said%20she%20was%20undergoing%20treatment%20for%20depression.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%20lived%20in%20Mumbai%20with%20her%20husband%2C%20Chandramani%20Jhangad%2C%20an%20animation%20engineer.%20She%20went%20to%20Bhagalpur%20to%20attend%20her%20sister's%20wedding%20on%20April%2018.%20Her%20husband%20returned%20home%20after%20the%20wedding%20but%20Amrita%20chose%20to%20stay%20back.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%20has%20been%20alongside%20Bhojpuri%20star%20Khesari%20Lal%20Yadav%20in%20'%3Cem%3EDeewanapan%3C%2Fem%3E'.%20She%20also%20acted%20in%20Hindi%20movies%2C%20TV%20shows%20and%20web%20series.%20She%20is%20also%20known%20for%20her%20role%20in%20the%20web%20series%20%3Cem%3E'Parishodh'.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECity%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%2C%20Shri%20Raj%2C%20said%20we%20will%20conduct%20a%20high-level%20investigation%20into%20this%20case.%20A%20team%20has%20been%20formed%2C%20the%20family%20members%20are%20being%20interrogated%20and%20further%20action%20is%20underway%20in%20the%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ctable%3E%3Cthead%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Cth%20colspan%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3EHelplines%3C%2Fth%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Fthead%3E%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3EVandrevala%20Foundation%20for%20Mental%20Health%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22tel%3A%2B919999666555%5C%22%3E9999666555%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ahelp%40vandrevalafoundation.com%5C%22%3Ehelp%40vandrevalafoundation.com%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3ETISS%20iCall%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22tel%3A%2B912225521111%5C%22%3E022-25521111%3C%2Fa%3E%20(Monday-Saturday%3A%208%20am%20to%2010%20pm)%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%20%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3E(If%20you%20need%20support%20or%20know%20someone%20who%20does%2C%20please%20reach%20out%20to%20your%20nearest%20mental%20health%20specialist.)%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%