of%20the%20PMLA%20(Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act)%20deals%20with%20the%20power%20of%20ED%20officials%20to%20issue%20summons%20and%20production%20of%20documents%2C%20evidence%20and%20other%20materials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20petition%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20has%20argued%20that%20his%20arrest%20is%20illegal%20and%20so%20is%20his%20custody.%20Its%20motive%20was%20political%2C%20made%20clear%20by%20the%20timing%20-%20ahead%20of%20the%20general%20elections.%20%26quot%3BThe%20attempt%20is%20to%20decimate%20a%20political%20party%20and%20topple%20an%20elected%20government%20of%20the%20NCT%20of%20Delhi%2C%26quot%3B%20his%20plea%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20Monday's%20hearing%2C%20his%20counsel%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi%20told%20the%20court%20that%20one%20can%20be%20arrested%20only%20on%20evidence%20of%20guilt%2C%20%26quot%3Bnot%20mere%20suspicion%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20also%20the%20threshold%20in%20Section%2045%20PMLA%20(law%20against%20money%20laundering)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20the%20investigating%20agency%20had%20not%20recoded%20the%20statement%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-tells-supreme-court-why-he-filed-no-bail-petition-5549397%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%20Asks%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20Why%20He%20Didn't%20Seek%20Bail%2C%20His%20Reply%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAre%20you%20not%20contradicting%20yourself%20by%20saying%20that%20his%20statements%20under%20Section%2050%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA)%20were%20not%20recorded%3F%20You%20don't%20appear%20on%20summons%20for%20recording%20of%20statements%20under%20Section%2050%20and%20then%20you%20say%20it%20was%20not%20recorded%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said%2C%20questioning%20what%20the%20investigating%20officer%20could%20do%20if%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20did%20not%20appear%20despite%20repeated%20summons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNon-recording%20of%20Section%2050%20statements%20is%20not%20a%20defence%20to%20arrest%20me%20for%20reasons%20of%20believing%20there%20is%20guilt%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singhvi%20had%20responded.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20saying%20other%20materials%20also%20do%20not%20establish%20my%20guilt.%20The%20ED%20came%20to%20my%20house%20to%20arrest%20me.%20Then%20why%20can't%20ED%20record%20my%20statement%20under%20Section%2050%20at%20my%20house%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20has%20skipped%20summons%20for%20questioning%20nine%20times%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20had%20said%20in%20its%20affidavit%20to%20the%20court.%20%26quot%3BToday%2C%20you%20cannot%20say%20that%20we%20will%20arrest%20you%20because%20you%20did%20not%20appear%20on%20summons.%20Can%20you%20say%20that%20since%20you%20did%20not%20cooperate%2C%20you%20will%20be%20arrested%3F%20Non-cooperation%20cannot%20be%20a%20ground%20for%20criminality%20or%20grounds%20of%20arrest.%20This%20court%20held%20last%20year%20that%20non-cooperation%20cannot%20be%20a%20ground%20of%20arrest%20under%20the%20PMLA%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singhvi%20told%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20last%20year%2C%20on%20April%2016%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20was%20questioned%20by%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20and%20answered%20all%20their%20queries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20has%20contended%20that%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20was%20avoiding%20interrogation%20and%20while%20recording%20his%20statement%20under%20Section%2017%20of%20the%20PMLA%2C%20he%20was%20evasive%20and%20uncooperative.%20Arrested%20on%20March%2021%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20was%20in%20the%20custody%20of%20the%20agency%20for%20questioning.%20He%20was%20moved%20to%20Tihar%20jail%20under%20judicial%20custody%20on%20April%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20had%20upheld%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20arrest%2C%20saying%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20was%20left%20with%20%26quot%3Blittle%20option%26quot%3B%20after%20he%20skipped%20repeated%20summons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20has%20contended%20that%20liquor%20companies%20were%20involved%20in%20framing%20of%20the%20Delhi%20excise%20policy%20of%202021-22%20that%20was%20subsequently%20scrapped.%20The%20policy%2C%20which%20would%20have%20brought%20them%20a%2012%20per%20cent%20profit%2C%20was%20framed%20after%20receiving%20kickbacks%20from%20a%20liquor%20lobby%20it%20dubbed%20the%20%26quot%3BSouth%20Group%26quot%3B.%20The%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20alleged%20the%20kickbacks%20were%20laundered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hearing%20will%20continue%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714441260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fkacr7vh_arvind-kejriwal_625x300_27_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-courts-strong-remarks-on-arvind-kejriwals-appeal-against-arrest-5553626%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20challenge%20to%20his%20arrest%20despite%20his%20refusal%20to%20give%20a%20statement%20to%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20in%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy%20case%20was%20questioned%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Monday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-courts-strong-remarks-on-arvind-kejriwals-appeal-against-arrest-5553626%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-courts-strong-remarks-on-arvind-kejriwals-appeal-against-arrest-5553626%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-courts-strong-remarks-on-arvind-kejriwals-appeal-against-arrest-5553626%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20U-Turn%2C%20AstraZeneca%20Admits%20Its%20Covishield%20Vaccine%20Can%20Cause%20Side%20Effect%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBritish%20pharma%20giant%20AstraZeneca%20has%20admitted%20that%20its%20Covid%20vaccine%20can%20cause%20a%20rare%20side%20effect%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Fnews%2F2024%2F04%2F28%2Fastrazeneca-admits-covid-vaccine-causes-rare-side-effect%2F%5C%22%3EThe%20Telegraph%20(UK)%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20reported.%20Covishield%20can%20cause%2C%20in%20rare%20cases%2C%20a%20condition%20that%20leads%20to%20blot%20clots%20and%20low%20platelet%20count%2C%20the%20vaccine-maker%20has%20said%20in%20court%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECovishield%2C%20developed%20by%20AstraZeneca%20and%20Oxford%20University%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20was%20produced%20by%20the%20Serum%20Institute%20of%20India%20and%20widely%20administered%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAstraZeneca%20is%20facing%20a%20class%20action%20lawsuit%20in%20the%20UK%20over%20claims%20that%20its%20vaccine%20caused%20deaths%20and%20severe%20injuries%20in%20several%20cases.%20Victims%20in%20as%20many%20as%2051%20cases%20in%20the%20UK%20High%20Court%20are%20seeking%20damages%20up%20to%20100%20million%20pounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJamie%20Scott%2C%20the%20first%20complainant%20in%20the%20case%2C%20had%20alleged%20that%20he%20had%20received%20the%20vaccine%20in%20April%202021%20which%20caused%20him%20a%20permanent%20brain%20injury%20after%20a%20blood%20clot.%20This%20has%20prevented%20him%20from%20working%20and%20the%20hospital%20even%20told%20his%20wife%20thrice%20that%20he's%20going%20to%20die%2C%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAstraZeneca%20has%20contested%20the%20claims%2C%20but%20admitted%20in%20one%20of%20the%20court%20documents%20in%20February%20that%20Covishield%20can%20%26quot%3Bin%20very%20rare%20cases%2C%20cause%20TTS%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETTS%20(Thrombosis%20with%20Thrombocytopenia%20Syndrome)%20causes%20blood%20clots%20and%20a%20low%20blood%20platelet%20count%20in%20humans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20admitted%20that%20the%20AZ%20vaccine%20can%2C%20in%20very%20rare%20cases%2C%20cause%20TTS.%20The%20causal%20mechanism%20is%20not%20known...Further%2C%20TTS%20can%20also%20occur%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20the%20AZ%20vaccine%20(or%20any%20vaccine).%20Causation%20in%20any%20individual%20case%20will%20be%20a%20matter%20for%20expert%20evidence%2C%26quot%3B%20AstraZeneca%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAstraZeneca%20made%20its%20admission%20in%20a%20legal%20defence%20to%20Scott's%20claim%2C%20which%20may%20lead%20to%20payouts%20to%20the%20victims%20and%20grieving%20relatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20admission%20also%20contradicts%20the%20company's%202023%20stand%2C%20in%20which%20it%20had%20told%20the%20lawyers%20of%20Jamie%20Scott%20that%20%26quot%3Bwe%20do%20not%20accept%20that%20TTS%20is%20caused%20by%20the%20vaccine%20at%20a%20generic%20level%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAstraZeneca%20has%2C%20however%2C%20denied%20the%20lawyers'%20claims%20that%20the%20vaccine%20is%20%26quot%3Bdefective%26quot%3B%20and%20its%20efficacy%20%26quot%3Bvastly%20overstated%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714441140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-03%2Fd53dn2b8_covishield-vaccine-india-afp_625x300_19_March_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fin-big-u-turn-astrazeneca-admits-its-covishield-vaccine-can-cause-side-effect-5553754%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22British%20pharma%20giant%20AstraZeneca%20has%20admitted%20that%20its%20Covid%20vaccine%20can%20cause%20a%20rare%20side%20effect%2C%20The%20Telegraph%20(UK)%20has%20reported.%20The%20side%20effect%2C%20the%20vaccine-maker%20has%20said%20in%20court%20documents.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fin-big-u-turn-astrazeneca-admits-its-covishield-vaccine-can-cause-side-effect-5553754%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2F