dson%20Prajwal%20Revanna%2C%20an%20accused%20in%20the%20alleged%20sex%20video%20scandal%2C%20will%20be%20asked%20to%20return%20to%20India%20by%20the%20Special%20Investigation%20Team%20(SIT)%2C%20said%20Karnataka%20Home%20Minister%20G.%20Parameshwara%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20media%20persons%2C%20Mr%20Parameshwara%20said%20that%20an%20SIT%20probe%20would%20be%20complete%20soon%20and%20a%20report%20is%20submitted%20within%2010%20to%2015%20days%20in%20such%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20this%20case%2C%20the%20directions%20have%20been%20given%20on%20the%20time%20frame%20to%20the%20investigation%20officers.%20If%20not%20for%20the%20time%20frame%2C%20the%20probe%20will%20be%20conducted%20for%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Home%20Minister%20said%20that%20an%20investigation%20would%20be%20conducted%20and%20action%20would%20be%20initiated%20against%20all%20the%20accused%20mentioned%20by%20the%20victims%20in%20the%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBased%20on%20the%20complaint%20to%20the%20Karnataka%20State%20Commission%20for%20Women%2C%20the%20state%20government%20has%20formed%20the%20SIT%20led%20by%20senior%20IPS%20officer%20B.K.%20Singh.%20Two%20women%20Superintendents%20of%20Police%20are%20also%20part%20of%20the%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20state%20government%20will%20not%20interfere%20in%20the%20probe%2C%20it%20is%20left%20to%20the%20probe%20agency%20to%20take%20it%20forward.%20The%20Investigating%20Officers%20will%20take%20the%20pen%20drives%20containing%20alleged%20sex%20videos%20which%20will%20be%20sent%20to%20the%20Forensic%20Science%20Laboratory%20(FSL)%20for%20verification.%20The%20evidence%20needed%20to%20be%20collected.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAccording%20to%20official%20information%2C%20the%20main%20accused%20Prajwal%20Revanna%20had%20travelled%20to%20a%20foreign%20country%2C%20he%20will%20be%20called%20back%20to%20India%20by%20the%20SIT%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Parameshwara%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20investigation%20would%20be%20conducted%20against%20JD(S)%20MLA%20H.D.%20Revanna%20against%20whom%20the%20complaint%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20is%20lodged%20separately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20SIT%20gives%20a%20report%2C%20the%20action%20would%20be%20initiated%20against%20the%20accused%20persons%2C%20the%20Home%20Minister%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SIT%20officers%20will%20probe%20the%20matter%20of%20the%20possibility%20of%20many%20more%20pen%20drives%20containing%20sex%20videos%20being%20prevented%20from%20being%20circulated%2C%20Mr%20Parameshwara%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government%20is%20ready%20to%20provide%20security%20to%20the%20complainants%20and%20victims%20if%20there%20is%20a%20necessity%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20mother-in-law%20of%20one%20of%20the%20victims%20has%20said%20that%20her%20daughter-in-law%20was%20quiet%20for%20five%20years%20and%20lodged%20a%20complaint%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBhavani%20madam%20(Prajwal%20Revanna's%20mother)%20has%20helped%20us%20and%20she%20stood%20with%20our%20family.%20She%20(daughter-in-law)%20was%20taken%20out%20forcefully%20and%20a%20complaint%20was%20lodged.%20It%20is%20being%20done%20to%20bring%20disrepute%20to%20the%20Deve%20Gowda%20family.%20This%20is%20a%20false%20complaint%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20SIT%20has%20expedited%20the%20probe%20and%20managed%20to%20locate%20five%20victims%20and%20received%20information%20from%20them%20after%20bringing%20them%20to%20the%20SIT%20office%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victims%20included%20government%20officers%20and%20political%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victims%20have%20recorded%20their%20statements%20in%20front%20of%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20Seema%20Latkar%2C%20sources%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20hea