n-pro-khalistan-event%2Farticleshow%2F109708322.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gaza%20Protesters%20Defy%20Columbia%20University's%20Deadline%20To%20Leave%20Campus%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EStudent%20demonstrators%20at%20Columbia%20University%2C%20the%20epicenter%20of%20pro-Palestinian%20protests%20that%20have%20erupted%20at%20US%20colleges%2C%20said%20Monday%20they%20would%20not%20budge%20until%20the%20school%20met%20their%20demands%2C%20defying%20an%20ultimatum%20to%20disperse%20or%20face%20suspension.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20350%20people%20were%20arrested%20at%20campuses%20across%20the%20United%20States%20over%20the%20weekend%2C%20with%20the%20White%20House%20calling%20on%20the%20demonstrations%20to%20remain%20peaceful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20at%20Columbia%20in%20New%20York%20issued%20a%20statement%20on%20Monday%20saying%20the%20protestors'%20encampment%20must%20be%20cleared%2C%20and%20rejecting%20a%20call%20to%20divest%20financial%20holdings%20linked%20to%20Israel%20--%20a%20key%20demand%20of%20demonstrators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20student%20protestors%20pushed%20back%2C%20vowing%20to%20defend%20their%20camp%20on%20the%20prestigious%20institution's%20main%20lawn%2C%20despite%20threats%20of%20suspensions%20and%20disciplinary%20action%20after%20a%202%3A00%20pm%20(1800%20GMT)%20deadline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20repulsive%20scare%20tactics%20mean%20nothing%20compared%20to%20the%20deaths%20of%20over%2034%2C000%20Palestinians%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20statement%2C%20read%20out%20by%20a%20student%20at%20a%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20not%20move%20until%20Columbia%20meets%20our%20demands%20or...%20are%20moved%20by%20force%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20student%2C%20who%20would%20not%20give%20his%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProtests%20against%20the%20Gaza%20war%2C%20with%20its%20high%20Palestinian%20civilian%20death%20toll%2C%20have%20posed%20a%20challenge%20to%20university%20administrators%20trying%20to%20balance%20free%20speech%20rights%20with%20complaints%20that%20the%20rallies%20have%20veered%20into%20anti-Semitism%20and%20hate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20almost%20two%20weeks%20now%20a%20wave%20of%20protests%20against%20Israel's%20war%20in%20Gaza%20has%20swept%20through%20US%20university%20campuses%20from%20coast%20to%20coast%2C%20after%20around%20100%20protesters%20were%20arrested%20at%20Columbia%20on%20April%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFootage%20of%20police%20in%20riot%20gear%20summoned%20at%20various%20colleges%20to%20break%20up%20rallies%20have%20been%20viewed%20around%20the%20world%2C%20recalling%20the%20protest%20movement%20that%20erupted%20during%20the%20Vietnam%20War.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Virginia%20Tech%2C%20more%20than%2090%20people%20were%20arrested%20late%20Sunday%20after%20refusing%20an%20order%20from%20campus%20police%20to%20disperse%2C%20while%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Texas%20state%20troopers%20in%20riot%20gear%20clashed%20Monday%20with%20protestors%20who%20attempted%20to%20set%20up%20an%20unauthorized%20encampment%20on%20the%20campus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20encampments%20will%20be%20allowed%2C%26quot%3B%20Texas%20Governor%20Greg%20Abbott%20said%20on%20social%20media.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInstead%2C%20arrests%20are%20being%20made%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20Talks%20break%20down%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EColumbia%20University%20president%20Minouche%20Shafik%2C%20in%20her%20statement%20announcing%20talks%20had%20broken%20down%2C%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bmany%20of%20our%20Jewish%20students%2C%20and%20other%20students%20as%20well%2C%20have%20found%20the%20atmosphere%20intolerable%20in%20recent%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20have%20left%20campus%2C%20and%20that%20is%20a%20tragedy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnti-Semitic%20language%20and%20actions%20are%20unacceptable%20and%20calls%20for%20violence%20are%20simply%20abhorrent%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProtest%20organizers%20deny%20accusations%20of%20anti-Semitism%2C%20arguing%20that%20their%20actions%20are%20aimed%20at%20the%20Israeli%20government%20and%20its%20prosecution%20of%20the%20conflict%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20insist%20some%20incidents%20have%20been%20engineered%20by%20non-student%20agitators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20school%20year%20wrapping%20up%2C%20administrators%20are%20also%20pointing%20to%20the%20need%20to%20maintain%20order%20on%20campus%20for%20exam%20studies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20group's%20rights%20to%20express%20their%20views%20cannot%20come%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20another%20group's%20right%20to%20speak%2C%20teach%20and%20learn%2C%26quot%3B%20Shafik%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20graduate%20student%20protester%2C%20who%20asked%20to%20be%20identified%20only%20as%20%26quot%3BZ%2C%26quot%3B%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20finals%20week%2C%20everyone%20is%20still%20working%20on%20their%20finals%2C%20I%20still%20have%20finals%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20school%20is%20temporary%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20protester%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Joe%20Biden's%20White%20House%20has%20also%20attempted%20to%20walk%20a%20fine%20line%20of%20defending%20the%20right%20to%20protest%20while%20condemning%20reported%20acts%20of%20anti-Semitism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20get%20that%20it%20is%20a%20painful%20moment%20that%20Americans%20are%20dealing%20with%2C%20and%20free%20expression%20has%20to%20be%20done%20within%20the%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20Press%20Secretary%20Karine%20Jean-Pierre%20said%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Biden's%20Republican%20opponents%20have%20seized%20on%20the%20issue%2C%20casting%20the%20protests%20as%20anti-Semitic%20and%20threatening%20to%20pull%20federal%20funding%20if%20they%20aren't%20stopped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%