d.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20if%20you%20nod%20at%20the%20prosecutors%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20Jesse%20Watters%20saying%20liberals%20have%20infiltrated%20the%20jury%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EJurors%20%3Cem%3Edid%3C%2Fem%3E%20look%20at%20Gotti%20Jr.%20and%20El%20Chapo%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJeffrey%20Lichtman%20has%20repped%20many%20mobsters%20and%20drug%20lords%20in%20his%20career.%20He%20wondered%20if%20jurors%20might%20be%20too%20intimidated%20to%20look%20at%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20John%20Gotti%20Jr.%2C%20and%20El%20Chapo%2C%20and%20it%20doesn't%20get%20any%20more%20intimidating%20than%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Lichtman%20said%20of%20two%20of%20his%20more%20famous%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJurors%20looked%20at%20both%20of%20%3Cem%3Ethem%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Gotti's%20federal%20racketeering%20charges%20were%20dropped%20after%20a%20third%20mistrial%20in%202006%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsinaloa-cartel-el-chapo-guzman-drug-trial-guilty-verdict-2019-2%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAfter%2520six%2520days%2520of%2520deliberations%2Cconspiracy%252C%2520and%2520use%2520of%2520firearms.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEl%20Chapo%20was%20convicted%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20drug%20trafficking%20and%20conspiracy%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20I%20think%20they%20looked%20at%20them%20as%20if%20they%20were%20animals%20in%20a%20zoo%2C%26quot%3B%20Lichtman%20conceded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20it's%20not%20uncommon%20for%20jurors%20to%20avoid%20looking%20at%20the%20defendant%2C%20said%20Lichtman%20and%20other%20trial-practice%20veterans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20potentially%20significant%2C%20they%20said%2C%20was%20that%20Trump%20was%20failing%20to%20look%20at%20his%20jury%2C%20at%20least%20not%20with%20anything%20approaching%20respect%20and%20appreciation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20imperative%20that%20he%20stop%20with%20the%20'Blue%20Steel'%20stare%2C%26quot%3B%20Lichtman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20want%20them%20to%20like%20you%2C%20and%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20intimidate%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20think%20you're%20being%20inconvenienced%20by%20being%20there%3F%20So%20are%20the%20jurors.%20This%20is%20an%20inconvenience%20for%20them%2C%20too.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223394%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20appears%20in%20court%20for%20opening%20statements%20in%20his%20Manhattan%20hush-money%20trial%20on%20April%2022%2C%202024.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66266e3423b29110d3015779%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222263%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDonald%20Trump%20in%20court%20for%20opening%20statements%20in%20his%20Manhattan%20hush-money%20trial.%3Cp%3EYuki%20Iwamura-Pool%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20enough%20for%20defense%20lawyer%20Todd%20Blanche%20to%20say%20in%20opening%20statements%20that%20Trump%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20person%2C%20just%20like%20you%20and%20me.%26quot%3B%20They%20have%20to%20try%20to%20show%20the%20jurors%20this%2C%20not%20just%20tell%20them%2C%20Lichtman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20important%20that%20the%20jury%20see%20the%20defendant%20and%20the%20lawyers%20laughing%20and%20smiling%20together%20throughout%20the%20trial%2C%26quot%3B%20Lichtman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20very%20clear%20on%20Gotti%20and%20El%20Chapo%20that%20I%20would%20go%20up%20to%20them%20during%20the%20summation%20and%20put%20my%20arm%20around%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20touch%20them%2C%20you%20humanize%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20anyone%20wants%20to%20look%20at%20a%20guy's%20face%20who's%20scowling.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ENo%20'resting%20scowl%20face'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20defense%20team%20is%20doing%20him