0simultaneously%20knows%20that%20it%20might%20not%20be%20enough%20against%20the%20technologically%20advanced%20Israeli%20or%20US%20weapons%20in%20a%20potential%20conflict%2C%26quot%3B%20Khoueiry%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat's%20one%20reason%20Iran%20has%20placed%20its%20most%20sensitive%20installations%20in%20mountainous%20regions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20the%20April%2019%20Isfahan%20strike%20will%20likely%20make%20the%20Iranians%20think%20more%20in%20terms%20of%20countering%20Israel's%20radar-evading%20systems%20by%20improving%20their%20radar%20capabilities%20while%20continuing%20to%20improve%20their%20air%20defenses%2C%20especially%20because%20we%20did%20not%20see%20Iran's%20best%20air%20defense%20equipment%20on%20display%2C%26quot%3B%20Khoueiry%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20S-300PMU-2%20is%20the%20most%20advanced%20air%20defense%20system%20Iran%20has%20acquired%20from%20Russia.%20Following%20the%20Isfahan%20strike%2C%20it's%20likely%20Tehran%20will%20conclude%20it%20needs%20more%20advanced%20Russian%20systems%2C%20such%20as%20the%20S-400%20they've%20by%20some%20accounts%20been%20asking%20for.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKhoueiry%20doesn't%20rule%20out%20the%20prospect%20of%20Iran%20seeking%20the%20S-400%2C%20given%20its%20%26quot%3Bmore%20advanced%20stealth%20capabilities%26quot%3B%20and%20ability%20to%20track%20aircraft%20at%20lower%20altitudes.%20These%20capabilities%20are%20%26quot%3Bcrucial%26quot%3B%20for%20defending%20vital%20Iranian%20installations%2C%20especially%20given%20the%20S-300's%20failure%20to%20intercept%20Israeli%20weapons%20on%20April%2019.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EClemson%20University's%20Azizi%20believes%20an%20S-400%20acquisition%20remains%20%26quot%3Bcrucial%26quot%3B%20for%20Iran%20and%20one%20of%20its%20%26quot%3Bbest%20bets.%26quot%3B%20Therefore%2C%20he%20anticipates%20Tehran%20will%20continue%20pushing%20for%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%