%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20affidavit%20filed%20by%20the%20State%20Licensing%20Authority%2C%20Ayurvedic%20and%20Unani%20Services%2C%20stated%20that%20it%20has%20granted%20permission%20on%20April%2012%20to%20the%20Drug%20Inspector%2C%20Haridwar%20for%20filing%20a%20complaint%20against%20Divya%20Pharmacy%20and%20Patanjali%20Ayurved%20Ltd.%20for%20repeated%20violations%20of%20the%20Drugs%20and%20Magic%20Remedies%20(Objectionable%20Advertisements)%20Act%2C%201954.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20SLA%20issued%20an%20order%2C%20dated%20April%2015%2C%202024%2C%20to%20Divya%20Pharmacy%20and%20Respondent%20No.%205-Patanjali%20Ayurved%20Ltd.%2C%20stating%20therein%20that%20the%20manufacturing%20licenses%20for%2014%20of%20their%20products%2C%20namely%20'Swasari%20Gold'%2C%20'Swasari%20Vati%2C%20Bronchom'%2C%20'Swasari%20Pravahi'%2C%20'Swasari%20Avaleh'%2C%20'MuktaVati%20Extra%20Power'%2C%20'Lipidom'%2C%20'Bp%20Grit'%2C%20'Madhugrit'%2C%20'MadhunashiniVati%20Extra%20Power'%2C%20'Livamrit%20Advance'%2C%20'Livogrit'%2C%20'Eyegrit%20Gold'%20and%20'Patanjali%20Drishti%20Eye%20Drop'%2C%20are%20suspended%20with%20immediate%20effect%20under%20Rule%20159(1)%20of%20The%20Drugs%20and%20Cosmetics%20Rules%2C%201945%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20District%20Ayurvedic%20and%20Unani%20Officer%2C%20Haridwar%20filed%20a%20criminal%20complaint%20before%20the%20Chief%20Judicial%20Magistrate%2C%20Haridwar%20against%20Swami%20Ramdev%2C%20Acharya%20Balkrishna%2C%20Divya%20Pharmacy%20and%20Patanjali%20Ayurved%20Limited%20under%20Sections%203%2C%204%20and%207%20of%20the%20Drugs%20and%20Magic%20Remedies%20(Objectionable%20Advertisements)%20Act%2C%201954%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20affidavit%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SLA%20said%20that%20it%20will%20continue%20to%20take%20all%20due%20and%20further%20steps%20against%20Divya%20Pharmacy%20and%20Patanjali%20Ayurved%20Ltd%2C%20as%20per%20the%20procedure%20prescribed%20in%20law%20and%20the%20directions%20issued%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20order%20passed%20on%20April%2010%2C%20the%20top%20court%20had%20ordered%20the%20then%20Joint%20Director%20of%20the%20State%20Licencing%20Authority%20and%20all%20the%20officers%20holding%20the%20post%20of%20District%20Ayurvedic%20and%20Unani%20Officer%2C%20Haridwar%20from%202018%20till%20date%20to%20file%20their%20respective%20affidavits%20explaining%20the%20inaction%20on%20their%20part.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Medical%20Association%20has%20sought%20action%20against%20Patanjali%20for%20violation%20of%20the%20Drugs%20and%20Magic%20Remedies%20(Objectionable%20Advertisements)%20Act%2C%20which%20prohibits%20the%20advertisement%20of%20certain%20products%20for%20the%20treatment%20of%20specified%20diseases%20and%20disorders%2C%20including%20diabetes%2C%20heart%20diseases%2C%20high%20or%20low%20blood%20pressure%20and%20obesity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ayurvedic%20company%20had%20earlier%20made%20an%20undertaking%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20saying%20that%20it%20would%20not%20make%20any%20casual%20statements%20claiming%20the%20medicinal%20efficacy%20of%20its%20products%20or%20advertise%20or%20brand%20them%20in%20violation%20of%20law%20and%20would%20not%20release%20any%20statement%20against%20any%20system%20of%20medicine%20to%20the%20media%20in%20any%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714415160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F95d28m2g_patanjali-generic_625x300_16_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flicenses-of-14-patanjali-products-cancelled-by-uttarakhand-authority-5552391%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Uttarakhand%20government%2C%20in%20an%20affidavit%2C%20told%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20it%20has%20suspended%20manufacturing%20licenses%20for%2014%20Pa