%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fduchess-of-edinburgh-sophie-becomes-first-member-of-royal-family-to-visit-ukraine-since-russias-invasion-13125922%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fduchess-of-edinburgh-sophie-becomes-first-member-of-royal-family-to-visit-ukraine-since-russias-invasion-13125922%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fduchess-of-edinburgh-sophie-becomes-first-member-of-royal-family-to-visit-ukraine-since-russias-invasion-13125922%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNo%20Congress%20Poster%20On%20Delhi's%207%20Seats%26quot%3B%3A%20Arvinder%20Lovely%20Points%20To%20AAP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EArvinder%20Singh%20Lovely%2C%20who%20stepped%20down%20from%20the%20post%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Congress%20chief%2C%20has%20strongly%20refuted%20speculation%20that%20he%20is%20about%20to%20change%20camp%20and%20has%20been%20acting%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20the%20BJP.%20Asserting%20that%20he%20has%20not%20leaked%20his%20own%20resignation%20letter%20to%20the%20media%20or%20resigned%20from%20the%20primary%20membership%20of%20the%20party%2C%20Mr%20Lovely%20said%20he%20stepped%20down%20because%20he%20felt%20unequal%20to%20the%20task%20of%20sacking%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20being%20asked%20to%20remove%20leaders%20loyal%20to%20the%20Congress%20for%20generations.%20I%20couldn't%20do%20that...%C2%A0%20A%20party%20should%20reach%20out%20to%20disgruntled%20people%2C%20not%20alienate%20them%20further%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20his%20bigger%20grouse%20--%20the%20Congress%20tie-up%20with%20longtime%20rival%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20in%20Delhi%20--%20Mr%20Lovely%20indicated%20that%20the%20alliance%20was%20costing%20the%20Congress%20its%20own%20turf.%20Under%20the%20deal%20to%20share%20the%20seven%20seats%20in%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20AAP%20is%20contesting%20four%20seats%20and%20the%20Congress%20three.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20%26quot%3Bin%20none%20of%20the%20seven%20seats%20of%20Delhi%2C%20Congress%20leaders'%20posters%20are%20up.%20AAP%20is%20not%20even%20using%20a%20single%20poster%20of%20Congress%20in%20the%20seats%20of%20Delhi%20it%20is%20contesting%20from%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20declaring%20that%20after%20readying%20the%20Congress%20state%20unit%20for%20the%20alliance%2C%20he%20is%20%26quot%3Bfacing%20insults%20now%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Delhi%20Congress%20--%20swept%20out%20of%20power%20by%20the%20anti-corruption%20campaign%20led%20by%20Anna%20Hazare%20and%20AAP%20leaders%20even%20before%20the%20party%20was%20formed%20--%20a%20tie-up%20with%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20is%20anathema.%20Their%20stiff%20resistance%20had%20scuttled%20the%20Opposition's%20unity%20efforts%20in%202019.%20But%20with%20the%20Opposition%20call%20to%20present%20a%20united%20front%20this%20time%2C%20the%20two%20parties%20have%20come%20on%20board%20with%20a%20seat-sharing%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unity%2C%20though%2C%20stops%20at%20the%20borders%20of%20Delhi.%20In%20Punjab%20and%20elsewhere%2C%20the%20two%20parties%20have%20fielded%20candidates%20against%20each%20other%2C%20throwing%20to%20the%20winds%20the%20plan%20of%20one-on-one%20contests%20that%20many%20Opposition%20leaders%20agreed%20was%20the%20only%20way%20to%20defeat%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Lovely%2C%20who%20went%20to%20show%20support%20for%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20after%20his%20arrest%2C%20said%20today%20that%20he%20was%20only%20carrying%20out%20the%20party%20high%20command's%20orders.%20%26quot%3BI%20always%20toed%20the%20high%20command's%20line%20%E2%80%93%20till%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20letter%20to%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20Mr%20Lovely%20had%20pointed%20to%20the%20jailing%20of%20several%20AAP%20ministers%20in%20connection%20to%20corruption%20cases.%20Despite%20that%2C%20the%20Congress%