%20wish%20is%20that%20Rinku%20makes%20it%20to%20the%20team.%20I%20will%20be%20so%20happy.%20That%20will%20be%20the%20high%20point%20for%20me.%26quot%3B%20With%20the%20KKR%20top-order%20doing%20the%20bulk%20of%20scoring%20so%20far%20this%20season%2C%20Rinku%20has%20not%20got%20many%20opportunities%20with%20the%20bat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20debut%20season%20however%2C%20the%20hard-hitting%20batsman%20from%20Aligarh%20amassed%20356%20runs%20in%2015%20matches%2C%20remaining%20unbeaten%20in%20seven%20of%20those%20games.%20His%20runs%20came%20at%20a%20strike-rate%20of%20over%20175%20but%20power-hitting%20is%20not%20his%20only%20talent%2C%20for%20he%20has%20the%20ability%20to%20remain%20calm%20in%20pressure%20situations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bollywood%20megastar%2C%20who%20shares%20a%20great%20rapport%20with%20Rinku%2C%20is%20delighted%20at%20his%20rise%20after%20having%20faced%20many%20obstacles%20on%20his%20road%20to%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%20in%20modest%20surroundings%2C%20Rinku's%20family%20struggled%20to%20make%20ends%20meet%2C%20with%20his%20father%20working%20as%20an%20LPG%20cylinder%20delivery%20man%20and%20his%20mother%20a%20housewife.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20offer%20of%20a%20job%20as%20a%20sweeper%2C%20Rinku%20followed%20his%20passion%20for%20cricket%2C%20believing%20it%20would%20lead%20him%20to%20greater%20heights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESRK%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20just%20want%20them%20to%20feel%20happy%20and%20when%20I%20see%20these%20boys%20playing%2C%20I%20feel%20like%20I%20am%20living%20as%20a%20sportsperson%20myself.%20Especially%20players%20like%20Rinku%20and%20Nitish%20(Rana)%2C%20I%20see%20myself%20in%20them.%20I%20feel%20really%20happy%20when%20they%20perform%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714409580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fh9snjptg_a_625x300_29_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fshah-rukh-khan-wi