on%20in%20Kerala%20took%20place%20on%20April%2026.%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20constituency%2C%20Wayanad%2C%20is%20located%20in%20the%20state%20and%20there%20was%20a%20buzz%20that%20the%20Congress%20would%20announce%20its%20candidate%20once%20the%20Kerala%20polls%20were%20over.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThere%20is%20expectation%20among%20the%20Congress's%20rank%20and%20file%20that%20Mr%20Gandhi%20would%20make%20an%20attempt%20to%20win%20back%20Amethi%20while%20his%20sister%2C%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%2C%20would%20step%20into%20her%20mother's%20shoes%20in%20Raebareli.%20There%20are%20those%2C%20though%2C%20who%20expect%20the%20party%20might%20flip%20the%20constituencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20whom%20she%20would%20prefer%20as%20opponent%20between%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20his%20sister%2C%20Ms%20Irani%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BCouldn't%20care%20less.%20Whoever%20comes%20will%20be%20defeated%20surely%2C%20because%20both%20these%20entities%20have%20been%20absentee%20politicians%20from%20the%20area.%20One%20has%20been%20an%20MP%2C%20missing%20for%2015%20years.%20I%20have%20worked%20for%20five%20years%2C%20two%20years%20of%20which%20were%20corona%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20tough%20time%20the%20constituency%20had%20passed%20through%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20talk%20about%20corona%2C%20people%20wonder%20why%20they%20(the%20Gandhis)%20were%20not%20around%20to%20help%20anyone%20in%20Amethi%20and%20Raebareli%20for%20that%20matter%26quot%3B.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20people%2C%20she%20added%2C%20%26quot%3Brealise%20if%20it%20was%20not%20for%20Prime%20Minister's%20benevolence%20in%20ensuring%20every%20citizen%20gets%20free%20ration%2C%20many%20people%20would%20have%20faced%20much%20difficulty%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20also%20understand%20that%20if%20not%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%2C%20nobody%20would%20have%20ensured%20that%20three%20vaccines%20were%20made%20available%