andal%3A%20HD%20Kumaraswamy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EJD(S)%20leader%20HD%20Kumaraswamy%20on%20Monday%20said%20the%20party%20has%20decided%20to%20suspend%20Prajwal%20Revanna%2C%20his%20nephew%20and%20Hassan%20MP%20who%20is%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20poll%20candidate%20in%20the%20current%20elections%2C%20over%20allegations%20of%20his%20sexual%20abuse%20of%20several%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20chief%20minister%20also%20sought%20to%20distance%20JD(S)'s%20alliance%20partner%20BJP%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20from%20the%20case%2C%20amid%20attacks%20by%20the%20ruling%20Congress%20seeking%20their%20response%20on%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Prajwal%20is%20the%20BJP-JD(S)%20alliance%20candidate%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20from%20Hassan%20constituency%2C%20which%20went%20to%20the%20polls%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20decision%20was%20already%20made.%20Tomorrow%20it%20is%20to%20be%20recommended%20at%20the%20core%20committee%20meeting%20in%20Hubballi.%20Because%20he%20(Prajwal)%20is%20a%20Member%20of%20Parliament%2C%20it%20has%20to%20be%20done%20from%20Delhi.%20So%20I%20had%20requested%20Deve%20Gowda%20(JD(S)%20National%20President%20and%20former%20PM).%20Neither%20he%20(Gowda)%20nor%20I%20were%20aware%20of%20this%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kumaraswamy%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%2C%20the%20JD(S)%20state%20chief%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSome%20issues%20that%20have%20come%20out%2C%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20that%20it%20has%20been%20decided%20yesterday%20itself%20to%20suspend%20(him).%20But%20many%20were%20in%20a%20hurry.%26quot%3B%20The%2033-year-old%20Prajwal%20Revanna%20is%20the%20son%20of%20HD%20Revanna%2C%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20JD(S)%20patriarch%20HD%20Deve%20Gowda's%20elder%20son%20who%20is%20an%20MLA%20and%20former%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20explicit%20video%20clips%20allegedly%20involving%20Prajwal%20Revanna%20sexually%20abusing%20several%20women%20started%20making%20the%20rounds%20in%20Hassan%20in%20recent%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20constituted%20a%20Special%20Investigation%20Team%20(SIT)%20to%20probe%20the%20alleged%20sex%20scandal%20involving%20the%20MP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumaraswamy%20said%20that%20in%20his%20opinion%2C%20along%20with%20the%20SIT%20investigating%20the%20sexual%20abuse%20allegations%20against%20Prajwal%20Revanna%2C%20what%20also%20needs%20to%20be%20inquired%20into%20is%20where%20the%20pen-drives%20(containing%20alleged%20explicit%20video%20clips)%20were%20created%20and%20who%20circulated%20it%20in%20large%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20far%2C%20there%20are%20no%20direct%20allegations%20against%20Prajwal%20Revanna.%20If%20the%20charges%20are%20true...punishment%20should%20happen%20in%20accordance%20with%20law.%20There%20is%20no%20compromise.%20If%20Prajwal%20Revanna%20is%20wrong%2C%20our%20family%20is%20in%20agreement%20for%20action%20to%20be%20taken%20against%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20Congress%20leaders%20trying%20to%20target%20BJP%20and%20PM%20Modi%20on%20the%20issue%2C%20Mr%20Kumaraswamy%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BDid%20PM%20Modi%20come%20for%20Prajwal%20Revanna's%20campaigning%3F%20What%20does%20PM%20Modi%20have%20to%20do%20with%20this%20case%3F%20What%20does%20the%20BJP%20have%20to%20do%20with%20this%3F%20Why%20link%20this%20with%20them%3F%20What%20does%20Deve%20Gowda%20or%20Kumaraswamy%20have%20to%20do%20with%20this%3F%26quot%3B%20Earlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20Mr%20Kumaraswamy%20said%20there%20is%20no%20question%20of%20defending%20Prajwal%20Revanna%20and%20that%20the%20party%20would%20take%20%26quot%3Bmerciless%20action%26quot%3B%20if%20the%20SIT%20probe%20proves%20the%20charges%20against%20the%20MP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20strongly%20objected%20to%20the%20names%20of%20his%20father%20Deve%20Gowda%2C%20among%20other%20family%20members%2C%20being%20drawn%20into%20the%20controversy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20ask%20Congress%20leaders%2C%20why%20bring%20family%20into%20it%3F%20Discuss%20about%20the%20individual.%20An%20individual%20and%20his%20deeds%20are%20in%20question%20here%2C%20not%20the%20family...why%20bring%20the%20family's%20name%2C%20Deve%20Gowda's%20name%20or%20Kumaraswamy's%20name%3F%20I%20have%20myself%20said%20whoever%20has%20committed%20the%20mistake%20has%20to%20undergo%20punishment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20such%20incidents%20cause%20embarrassment%20to%20the%20society%20as%20a%20whole%2C%20Mr%20Kumaraswamy%20said%20there%20is%20no%20question%20of%20defending%20anyone.%20%26quot%3BWrong%20is%20wrong%2C%20irrespective%20of%20who%20has%20committed%20it.%26quot%3B%20The%20police%20have%20information%20that%20Prajwal%20has%20left%20the%20country%2C%20according%20to%20a%20statement%20issued%20by%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20Office%2C%20which%20announced%20the%20SIT%20probe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20Mr%20Prajwal's%20whereabouts%2C%20Mr%20Kumaraswamy%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20should%20I%20say%2C%20if%20you%20ask%20me%3F%20Will%20he%20ask%20me%20and%20go%20anywhere...They%2C%20the%20government%2C%20will%20take%20action.%26quot%3B%20To%20a%20question%20whether%20he%20had%20no%20prior%20information%20about%20what%20was%20happening%2C%20he%20claimed%2C%20%26quot%3BWhere%20did%20we%20know%20about%20the%20matter%3F%20They%20(Revanna%20family)%20are%20separate.%20If%20it%20had%20come%20to%20our%20notice%20we%20could%20have%20taken%20action%20and%20stopped%20this%20embarrassment%20from%20happening.%20This%20matter%20is%20about%20an%20individual's%20background.%20Can%20we%20watch%20where%20he%20goes%20or%20comes%20every%20day%3F%20Is%20it%20in%20our%20hands%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20whether%20there%20is%20a%20political%20conspiracy%20behind%20the%20leak%20of%20the%20video%20clips%2C%20the%20JD(S)%20state%20chief%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThat%20is%20also%20there.%20Let's%20see.%20Let%20the%20SIT%20report%20come%20out.%20It%20is%20being%20said%20that%20the%20pen-drive%20(containing%20video%20clips)%20has%20been%20circulated.%20Some%20experts%20are%20behind%20it%2C%20let%20it%20come%20out.%26quot%3B%20He%20further%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20tell%20SIT%20and%20the%20government%20to%20conduct%20a%20fair%20probe.%20Such%20incidents%20should%20not%20happen%20in%20society%2C%20in%20my%20opinion%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20Deve%20Gowda%20and%20he%20have%20always%20conducted%20themselves%20with%20utmost%20respect%20towards%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20the%20development%20will%20have%20no%20impact%20on%20the%20results%2C%20Mr%20Kumaraswamy%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20Hassan%20the%20NDA%20candidate%20will%20win%3B%20there%20is%20no%20doubt%20about%20it.%26quot%3B%20He%20further%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20(Prajwal)%20will%20win%20with%20a%20good%20margin.%20But%20the%20developments%20that%20have%20taken%20place%20in%20the%20last%20few%20days%20have%20led%20to%20state-wide%20discussion.%20Who%20released%20(the%20video%20clippings)%2C%20a%20few%20days%20ago%2C%20what%20was%20the%20reason%20for%20releasing%20it%3F%20An%20old%20subject%20has%20been%20raised%20now%2C%20why%20didn't%20they%20raise%20the%20issue%20earlier%20but%20just%20days%20ahead%20of%20the%20election%3F...I%20don't%20want%20to%20discuss%20it%20much.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714406760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F8924j0d8_hd-kumaraswamy_625x300_05_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjd-s-to-suspend-deve-gowdas-grandson-over-sex-scandal-hd-kumaraswamy-5550146%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22JD(S)%20leader%20HD%20Kumaraswamy%20on%20Monday%20said%20the%20party%20has%20decided%20to%2