igure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Prefer%20grafted%20saplings%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20people%20would%20grow%20fruits%20from%20seeds%2C%20but%20this%20process%20takes%20five%20to%20seven%20years%20to%20give%20yield.%20In%20contrast%2C%20grafted%20plants%20give%20produce%20within%20a%20year.%20Initially%2C%20I%20plant%20the%20sapling%20into%20a%20small%20pot%20of%20say%2015%20inches%20before%20transferring%20it%20into%20the%20fish%20crates.%20After%20about%20a%20year%2C%20the%20plant%20will%20be%20root-bound%20enough%20to%20be%20shifted%20into%20a%20comparatively%20large%20fish%20crate%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Prepare%20the%20right%20soil%20mixture%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJayanti%20says%20preparing%20a%20perfect%20soil%20mix%20for%20pots%20is%20an%20extremely%20important%20step%20as%20its%20components%20act%20as%20true%20boosters%20for%20fruit%20trees%20that%20are%20typically%20grown%20in%20large%20farmland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20grow%20fruit%20trees%20on%20the%20terrace%2C%20you%20should%20prepare%20a%20lightweight%20potting%20mixture.%20Mix%2030%20percent%20garden%20soil%20with%2030%20percent%20cow%20dung%20compost%2C%2030%20percent%20cocopeat%2C%205%20percent%20of%20neem%20%3Cem%3Ekhali%3C%2Fem%3E%20(cake)%20powder%2C%20and%205%20percent%20of%20bonemeal%20powder.%20Before%20transferring%20the%20mix%20into%20the%20pot%2C%20place%20a%20thick%20layer%20(4-5%20inches)%20of%20dried%20leaves%20on%20the%20pot%20which%20will%20turn%20into%20compost%20later%20on%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20suggests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Add%20liquid%20fertiliser%20to%20boost%20growth%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20grown%20on%20a%20farm%2C%20trees%20take%20nutrients%20from%20the%20soil%2C%20but%20when%20we%20grow%20them%20in%20pots%2C%20we%20need%20to%20provide%20them%20with%20additional%20nutrients%20regularly%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jayanti.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FJayanti-Sahoo-1-1713363511.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jayanti%E2%80%99s%20techniques%20have%20helped%20her%20get%20sufficient%20fruits%20for%20the%20past%20three%20decades.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FJayanti-Sahoo-1-1713363511.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FJayanti-Sahoo-1-1713363511-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FJayanti-Sahoo-1-1713363511-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FJayanti-Sahoo-1-1713363511-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FJayanti-Sahoo-1-1713363511-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347571%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EJayanti%E2%80%99s%20techniques%20have%20helped%20her%20get%20sufficient%20fruits%20for%20the%20past%20three%20decades.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20provide%20additional%20nutrients%2C%20take%201%20kg%20mustard%20cake%20and%20250%20grams%20of%20neem%20%3Cem%3Ekhali%20%3C%2Fem%3Epowder%20and%20mix%20it%20in%205%20litres%20of%20water.%20Stir%20it%20and%20then%20keep%20it%20under%20shade%20for%20five%20days.%20Mix%201%20litre%20of%20this%20liquid%20fertiliser%20in%2010%20litres%20of%20water%20and%20give%20the%20diluted%20fertiliser%20to%20the%20plant%20every%2015%20days.%20This%20liquid%20fertiliser%20helps%20boost%20the%20flowering%20and%20fruiting%20in%20the%20trees%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E6.%20Deal%20with%20pests%20early%20on%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJayanti%