s%20get%20to%20know%20the%20river)%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20few%20kilometres%2C%20the%20team%20members%20took%20soil%20and%20water%20samples%20and%20planted%20indigenous%20varieties%20of%20trees.%20They%20also%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20villagers%20living%20around%20the%20river%20and%20educated%20them%20on%20its%20dismal%20state.%20They%20also%20explained%20their%20vision%20and%20the%20steps%20to%20be%20taken%20to%20restore%20Manganga.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20result%20of%20the%2021-day%20trip%20was%20a%20slim%20book%20titled%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EParikrama%20Mangangechi%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(Circumnavigating%20Manganga)%20which%20highlighted%20the%20status%20of%20the%20river%20and%20was%20sold%20to%20school%20and%20college%20libraries%2C%20students%2C%20professionals%20and%20farmers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FGhongade-second-from-left-with-villagers_11zon-1713963632.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ghongade%20(second%20from%20left)%20and%20some%20members%20of%20the%20team%20of%20experts%20and%20locals%20who%20helped%20revive%20the%20Manganga%20river.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FGhongade-second-from-left-with-villagers_11zon-1713963632.jpg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FGhongade-second-from-left-with-villagers_11zon-1713963632-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FGhongade-second-from-left-with-villagers_11zon-1713963632-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FGhongade-second-from-left-with-villagers_11zon-1713963632-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FGhongade-second-f